      "span_text": "Inventory. * rw would deny access to Smith, while permitting all other members of the \"Inventory\" project to read and write the segment. [CITATION_1] To insure that such control is effective, when an entry is added to an access control list, it is sorted into the list according to how specific the entry is by the following rule: all entries containing specific names in the first part are placed before those with \"don't cares\" in the first part.",
